    ToolCallEvent --> AgentIdentity : contains
    AuditRecord --> ToolCallEvent : maps event fields
    AuditRecord --> PolicyDecision : maps decision fields
    AuditRecord --> AgentIdentity : maps identity fields
    F014 --> AuditRecord : creates via factory
    F017 --> AuditRecord : returns in API
    F019 --> AuditRecord : renders feed/table
    F030 --> AuditRecord : stores in ClickHouse

    note for AuditRecord "Factory flow:\n1) Caller invokes from_event_and_decision(event, decision, payload)\n2) Factory reads event and agent identity fields\n3) Factory reads policy decision fields\n4) Factory returns frozen AuditRecord"
